data.title: Typical Subway
data.text: Very fast, but there is a lot of on-line orders that might make the wait a little more.  Nothing special.  Excellent service.

data.title: my favorite
data.text: I love there sub rolls and the choice of veggie's and sauces. I like the fact that I can buy a foot long sub for 5.00$ and split it with my daughter. It's a healthy fast food restaurant. Much healthier than some other fast food places I have visited in the past. I actually only go to subway nowadays. Nice place to go if on a budget.
